{"tid":1340380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警同MTR配合黑社會在元朗屠殺無辜市民","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T21:55:21.000Z","uid":274045,"like":191,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"41b3ed7bd72534c58d94cc13bde0739ee8171bab","tid":1340380,"uid":274045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:57:14.000Z","msg":"全程錄影證據<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=547539255780791&amp;id=534865589914032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D547539255780791%26id%3D534865589914032&d=PG0fnU9ECAVDedUX85NM%2FITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=443c2924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=547539255780791&amp;id=534865589914032</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">第一階段: 西鐵站外圍毆打市民，特別針對年輕人及有參與遊行的人士</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">第二階段: 西鐵站內毆打普通市民，有女士被打爆頭，滿地鮮血</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">第三階段: 衝上西鐵站二層月臺，再瘋狂襲擊列車內市民，入面有女人有細路!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屠殺30分鐘後，黑社會人士離開，一分鐘內警察剛好到場，警察與黑警擦肩而過，黑社會全身而退</span></span></strong></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9a3b69a3ad4b089365f1d391867a1b927f051d38","tid":1340380,"uid":1703,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"〔元朗站〕嚴重懷疑地鐵有份同黑社會合作<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1339911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1339911</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當時月台全部係白衫黑社會<br />\n<br />\n然後白衫見地鐵唔關門 就情緒失控<br />\n衝晒入地鐵車廂打人 見人就打<br />\n車廂全部都係尖叫聲同埋喊聲<br />\n有女仔嗌：我岩岩收工咋喎做咩要打我<br />\n<br />\n跟住有個男人跪係到求班白衫唔好再打人"},{"pid":"afaa134e92b6a89da4eb76b5220c1e83b18a4eef","tid":1340380,"uid":274045,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警黑勾結，必須付出代價，一個都不能活</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5cfc15e51bde4d464d74bf72e5f9f07ec1291d03","tid":1340380,"uid":274045,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:00:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警黑勾結，必須付出代價，一個都不能活</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3d90f6571ae10b120ac2f3b10e1633f6f0e56bd8","tid":1340380,"uid":274045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:02:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警黑勾結，必須付出代價，一個都不能活</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ef2f58ae6913b09f3b2a7da75bfd653be1628f54","tid":1340380,"uid":274045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:02:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警黑勾結，必須付出代價，一個都不能活</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a04cdde3cb7caa64b88f6315ba5a89eb398be43c","tid":1340380,"uid":274045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:02:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警黑勾結，必須付出代價，一個都不能活</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dc6d88bdd6ac4bc6bfb9937e171315ab5c57dbc9","tid":1340380,"uid":274045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:02:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警黑勾結，必須付出代價，一個都不能活</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"220158865808be9208c38fb4140da4e6635e9a4c","tid":1340380,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>黑社會=警察B隊</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"dc5e5ae199c11a166d5a563e9f4e5fe4b97334b8","tid":1340380,"uid":69742,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要報上國際新聞</span>"},{"pid":"3a92ced81e7bb542d4401964